  "texts": [
    "The extracted data included study characteristics (e.g., author(s), year of publication, country, field of publication), data sources, NLP techniques utilized, outcomes, challenges, and implications for hypertension research.",
    "We randomly selected 10 papers at the beginning for which all team members extracted data to calibrate.",
    "For the remaining papers, data extraction was performed by one reviewer and cross-verified by a second reviewer to ensure accuracy.",
    "Data Synthesis and AnalysisThe extracted data was synthesized using a narrative approach.",
    "Themes related to the types of unstructured data, NLP models, outcomes, challenges, and potential benefits were identified and summarized."
  ]
}